name: Daniel Rey Cimafranca
text: Well we've been here for several years now.  Scam capital of the world ata tayo.  It is expected that there will be people who will take advantage whatevr the ppolitical situation, regardless of who are in office.  So paano nga ba sila mahuhuli kung hindi ang pulis?    And yes dapat may nahuhuli.  Minority Report is just fiction ü  Once a person decides to kill someone it's difficult to prevent.  Dapat lang mahuli.
